<p>This month <italic>Perspectives in Public Health</italic> is pleased to share with you the variety of recent contributions we have received from RSPH members. We are always keen to hear your comments and views on all areas of public health and would welcome any contribution. The RSPH has recently launched the member’s forum in the member’s area of the website. Below you can read some of the posts we have received; please visit the RSPH website to add your view. We hope you enjoy reading what other members have to say, and look forward to hearing your response!</p>
